text: Darya Roga (born 3 July 1995) is a Kazakhstani female water polo player. She competed for the Kazakhstan women's national water polo team in the 2015 World Aquatics Championships, 2017 World Aquatics Championships, 2018 FINA Women's Intercontinental Tournament, and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites== *Darya Roga of Kazakhstan and Madeleine Steere of Australia Reuters Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani water polo players
